---
title: Mango Tango Chicken Tacos with Hot Sauce Crema
description: Tonight’s addictively sweet and savory tacos star mango in not one, but TWO ways. Mango juice simmers with spiced chicken breast strips and sautéed poblano and onion to form a sticky and satisfying filling, while chunks of the fruit are stirred into a refreshing salsa with onion, tomato, cilantro, and lime juice. This is one meal that’s just as pretty as it is to eat—taco ’bout a dinner winner!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/tropical-chicken-tacos-282edaf0.jpg
